text: Ok but there are actually little lizard dragons on this planet and I want one. Draco Volans. Look that shit up

Draco Volans lizard known as "flying dragon": Indonesian. Xenodermus known as "dragonsnake", first of its family: Indonesian. Earless Monitor, first of its family but related to monitors: Indonesian. Komodo dragon, largest living monitor: Indonesian.
